Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I'm on Page 02 of Thoracic CT
Then 'Indication' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Mass/Tumor' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Infection' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled
And 'Negative' radio button is enabled
And 'Positive' radio button is enabled
And 'Age of test in days' input field is enabled

When I select 'Interstitial lung disease' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Pulmonary artery embolism' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Pulmonary hypertension' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Pneumothorax' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Trauma' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled
